{"tid":1459860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"純討論 狗官落地獄","createTime":"2019-08-12T23:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T23:15:24.000Z","uid":255404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6687850a759c276a8ca9dab3289e41c23593e115","tid":1459860,"uid":255404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:02:57.000Z","msg":"雖然我係P牌仔 但有啲說話想同大家討論下<br />\n純討論！<br />\n如果有咩講錯可以用不推文應我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感激父母都淺黃 自己都有出去發夢做前線<br />\n黑警真係有好撚大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係到呢個時勢 心情每日都好抑壓<br />\n我覺得最撚9係政府 係林鄭月娥.<br />\n最近有同其他前線傾下計 <br />\n大家都覺到黑警係要搞 但首先其實要focus係政府到<br />\n雖然我都唔知有咩方法 黑警喪心病狂 <br />\n睇佢地個狗樣都仲覺得自己無問題有人保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今時今日 政府推黑警出黎 令警民關係一直差<br />\n最大得益唔係黑警 只係係背後恥笑緊一切既狗官<br />\n政府只係撐狗 令佢地有權力去搞我地 令到啲狗覺得自己做乜都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出post唔係想博啲咩 只係想搵人一齊思考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4077fdf94437796a5d241f987ba5360cd7cb39","tid":1459860,"uid":255404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:03:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"700fea7af98b5dfd3919dda6bd841090760256fc","tid":1459860,"uid":255404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:03:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e18321563608d9102cc418f7634e2567a72f931","tid":1459860,"uid":255404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:03:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e040037240f50b74916e59800e970fdfe72e5827","tid":1459860,"uid":255404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:04:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e63863f7c2793080c28abda39aec427973e812f","tid":1459860,"uid":255404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy